---
// CorporateSection.astro - Premium section for corporate ESG - Tailwind v4
---

<section id="per-aziende" class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-linear-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-950 to-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden">
	<!-- Background Elements -->
	<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-violet-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
	<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
		<!-- Section Header -->
		<div class="text-center mb-16 md:mb-20">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 bg-violet-500/20 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-violet-500/30">
				<span class="inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-violet-500"></span>
				<span class="text-violet-300 text-sm font-semibold">ESG Aziendale</span>
			</div>

			<h2 class="text-white mb-4 font-black tracking-tight text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
				<span class="block">Semplifica le tue</span>
				<span class="block bg-linear-to-r from-violet-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Iniziative ESG</span>
			</h2>
			<p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-slate-300 mt-6 leading-relaxed">
				Coinvolgi i tuoi dipendenti in cause significative, misura l'impatto ESG con trasparenza, 
				e costruisci una cultura aziendale orientata al cambiamento sociale.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Features Grid - Dark theme for corporate -->
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
			<!-- Feature 1: Iniziative di Team -->
			<div class="group rounded-3xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-violet-500/30 p-8 md:p-10 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-violet-500/20 hover:border-violet-500/60">
				<!-- Icon Container -->
				<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-linear-to-br from-violet-500/30 to-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform border border-violet-500/30">
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-violet-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 19H9a6 6 0 016-6h0a6 6 0 016 6v1"></path>
					</svg>
				</div>

				<!-- Title -->
				<h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3">Iniziative di Team</h3>

				<!-- Description -->
				<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Organizza volunteer day aziendali, raccogli iscrizioni e coordina le tue squadre. 
					Uno strumento per rafforzare lo spirito di team.
				</p>

				<!-- Link with arrow -->
				<div class="flex items-center text-violet-400 font-semibold text-sm group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
					Scopri di più
					<svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Feature 2: Tracciamento ESG -->
			<div class="group rounded-3xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-purple-500/30 p-8 md:p-10 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-purple-500/20 hover:border-purple-500/60">
				<!-- Icon Container -->
				<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-linear-to-br from-purple-500/30 to-violet-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform border border-purple-500/30">
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
					</svg>
				</div>

				<!-- Title -->
				<h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3">Tracciamento ESG</h3>

				<!-- Description -->
				<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Rapporti automatici su impatto sociale, ambientale e di governance. Metriche verificabili per 
					stakeholder e certificazioni ESG.
				</p>

				<!-- Link with arrow -->
				<div class="flex items-center text-purple-400 font-semibold text-sm group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
					Analytics Dashboard
					<svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Feature 3: Coinvolgimento Dipendenti -->
			<div class="group rounded-3xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-violet-500/30 p-8 md:p-10 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-violet-500/20 hover:border-violet-500/60">
				<!-- Icon Container -->
				<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-linear-to-br from-violet-500/30 to-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform border border-violet-500/30">
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-violet-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
					</svg>
				</div>

				<!-- Title -->
				<h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3">Coinvolgimento Dipendenti</h3>

				<!-- Description -->
				<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Aumenta l'engagement con programmi Purpose-Driven. Gamification, leaderboard e premi 
					per motivare la partecipazione.
				</p>

				<!-- Link with arrow -->
				<div class="flex items-center text-violet-400 font-semibold text-sm group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
					Vedi Programmi
					<svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Use Cases / Benefits -->
		<div class="mt-16 md:mt-24 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
			<!-- Left: Uses -->
			<div class="rounded-3xl bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700/50 p-10">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="inline-block w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-linear-to-br from-violet-500 to-purple-500 flex items-center justify-center">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
						</svg>
					</span>
					Metriche che Contano
				</h3>

				<ul class="space-y-4">
					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-violet-500/20 border border-violet-500/40 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-violet-400"></span>
						</span>
						<div>
							<p class="text-white font-semibold">Ore Volontariato Totali</p>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Aggregati in tempo reale da tutta la squadra</p>
						</div>
					</li>

					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-purple-400"></span>
						</span>
						<div>
							<p class="text-white font-semibold">Valore Sociale Generato</p>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Calcolato secondo metodologie internazionali</p>
						</div>
					</li>

					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-violet-500/20 border border-violet-500/40 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-violet-400"></span>
						</span>
						<div>
							<p class="text-white font-semibold">Partecipazione Dipendenti</p>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-400">% di coinvolgimento e engagement trends</p>
						</div>
					</li>

					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-purple-400"></span>
						</span>
						<div>
							<p class="text-white font-semibold">Allineamento con SDGs</p>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Mapping automatico con i Sustainable Development Goals</p>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- Right: Image / Illustration -->
			<div class="rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-purple-500/20 border border-violet-500/30 p-12 flex items-center justify-center">
				<div class="text-center">
					<div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-slate-900/80 border-4 border-violet-500/40 mb-4">
						<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-violet-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<p class="text-white font-semibold">ROI Sociale Certificato</p>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Rendicontazione trasparente</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- CTA Section -->
		<div class="mt-16 text-center">
			<p class="text-slate-300 mb-6 text-lg">Pronto a trasformare le tue iniziative ESG?</p>
			<a href="#contatti" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 bg-linear-to-r from-violet-600 to-purple-600 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-violet-500/30">
				Richiedi una Demo
				<svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
				</svg>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
